729143f-a.title: Richmond: Meredith Avenue - Chelsea Road
729143f-a.text:
Meredith Avenue, southeast from and past Chelsea Road. Chelsea Creek can be seen winding its course through the marshes
directly bebind the dead tree.
May 16, 1937
P. L. Sperr
